title: (Weds Full) The Show Competes in Blind Disney Karaoke! + Did We Win The Lottery?? Lunchbox Reveals It!
itunes:title: (Weds Full) The Show Competes in Blind Disney Karaoke! + Did We Win The Lottery?? Lunchbox Reveals It!
description:
We put 10 Disney songs on the wheel. Whatever song it lands on, the person has to perform the song but with NO LYRICS! We crown a winner of the game, and they win some cash for Blind Disney Karaoke. We get a big update from Lunchbox on whether we won in the lottery or not.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
